WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:01.218 --> 00:00:02.866
<i>Previously on</i> "Emerald City"...

2
00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.983
You are the only child of
Samuel and Katherine Pastoria.

3
00:00:06.031 --> 00:00:07.500
What kind of a name is Ozma?

4
00:00:07.570 --> 00:00:09.100
It means "leader of Oz."

5
00:00:09.148 --> 00:00:10.421
<i>Dorothy's not an assassin.</i>

6
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:12.726
<i>The Wizard sent her to kill me.</i>

7
00:00:12.812 --> 00:00:16.218
Take her life
and your heart will be free.

8
00:00:16.289 --> 00:00:17.296
Stop Glinda.

9
00:00:17.406 --> 00:00:18.921
But you have your giants.
Use them.

10
00:00:18.992 --> 00:00:20.903
<i>Their power is locked
in the prison of the abject.</i>

11
00:00:20.950 --> 00:00:23.857
Mistress east and I.
we had a partnership.

12
00:00:23.905 --> 00:00:26.092
Prison of the abject.
We can't unlock it.

13
00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:28.648
<i>A witch's spells are her own.</i>

14
00:00:31.797 --> 00:00:33.798
<i>I'm not drinking
a witch's insides.</i>

15
00:00:33.918 --> 00:00:35.567
You want revenge
for your parents.

16
00:00:35.661 --> 00:00:37.512
You want to destroy the Wizard.

17
00:00:37.590 --> 00:00:39.571
Then taste my sister's magic.

18
00:00:39.715 --> 00:00:40.989
Tip!

19
00:00:41.041 --> 00:00:43.675
Kill him!

20
00:00:48.615 --> 00:00:50.825
<i>♪ ♪</i>

21
00:00:51.098 --> 00:00:52.517
it worked.

22
00:00:52.622 --> 00:00:54.403
Are my weapons at the ready?

23
00:00:54.451 --> 00:00:55.917
Guards!

24
00:00:56.372 --> 00:00:57.768
You're joking.

25
00:01:02.062 --> 00:01:06.064
<i>♪ ♪</i>

26
00:01:06.489 --> 00:01:08.566
Turn around

27
00:01:08.668 --> 00:01:10.735
and no harm will come to you.

28
00:01:10.879 --> 00:01:13.395
I demand an audience
with the Queen!

29
00:01:13.536 --> 00:01:16.829
Not a captain of an army
who's never seen a fight!

30
00:01:17.004 --> 00:01:18.776
Then there will be harm.

31
00:01:18.981 --> 00:01:21.246
Those weapons that you have!

32
00:01:21.442 --> 00:01:24.723
They were manufactured
to outfit my men.

33
00:01:24.851 --> 00:01:26.885
The guns are ours.

34
00:01:28.794 --> 00:01:32.692
The people of ev.
they know I've been generous.

35
00:01:32.786 --> 00:01:37.595
And now the Queen will know
how grateful I am.

36
00:01:38.597 --> 00:01:41.333
Perhaps this payment

37
00:01:41.403 --> 00:01:44.869
will help the girl
come to her senses.

38
00:01:44.871 --> 00:01:51.042
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39
00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:53.184
let them in.

40
00:01:55.418 --> 00:01:57.549
Just the gold.

41
00:01:57.597 --> 00:02:04.702
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42
00:02:07.387 --> 00:02:10.123
he's doubled his payment.

43
00:02:11.830 --> 00:02:16.601
My Queen.
the beast is nearly upon us.

44
00:02:16.603 --> 00:02:18.770
You're dooming us
to repeat the past

45
00:02:18.818 --> 00:02:20.872
if the Wizard cannot defend us.

46
00:02:21.114 --> 00:02:25.076
The weapons are all the power
we need to defend ourselves.

47
00:02:27.067 --> 00:02:29.781
Let his kingdom
be destroyed this time.

48
00:02:31.356 --> 00:02:36.715
And let us take away any
currency he needs to rebuild it.

49
00:02:37.020 --> 00:02:39.591
You're making an enemy
of the Wizard.

50
00:02:42.956 --> 00:02:45.817
What would my father have done?

51
00:02:46.005 --> 00:02:48.138
Accept the payment.

52
00:02:49.446 --> 00:02:51.314
Then so will I.

53
00:02:54.262 --> 00:02:55.864
And I'll keep the guns.

54
00:02:55.942 --> 00:03:03.047
<i>♪ ♪</i>

55
00:03:05.958 --> 00:03:09.354
we have your gold.
We have your guns.

56
00:03:09.497 --> 00:03:12.824
We no longer need
the Wizard of oz.

57
00:03:15.372 --> 00:03:17.005
Don't go.

58
00:03:17.139 --> 00:03:18.706
You can't go.

59
00:03:18.770 --> 00:03:21.731
What am I supposed to do
without you?

60
00:03:21.903 --> 00:03:26.104
The pain...
It never stopped.

61
00:03:28.090 --> 00:03:29.566
Maybe on the other side...

62
00:03:29.614 --> 00:03:31.776
No.
I was just there.

63
00:03:32.020 --> 00:03:33.945
I saw my family.

64
00:03:36.176 --> 00:03:38.582
I felt them.

65
00:03:39.008 --> 00:03:41.341
how they loved me.

66
00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:46.791
I watched them murdered by a man
wearing the mask of a lion.

67
00:03:47.993 --> 00:03:50.816
I know every detail.

68
00:03:51.043 --> 00:03:52.997
That was death.

69
00:03:56.035 --> 00:03:58.670
Please don't become that.

70
00:04:01.309 --> 00:04:02.974
Please...

71
00:04:05.979 --> 00:04:12.984
<i>♪ ♪</i>

72
00:04:13.293 --> 00:04:16.888
my sister...

73
00:04:17.225 --> 00:04:20.548
Do you feel her inside you?

74
00:04:22.530 --> 00:04:24.999
What does she command?

75
00:04:25.678 --> 00:04:27.332
A message.

76
00:04:27.527 --> 00:04:29.801
For you.

77
00:04:30.199 --> 00:04:31.969
Tell me.

78
00:04:34.316 --> 00:04:38.120
She wants you to get up
off your sorry ass and help me.

79
00:04:39.732 --> 00:04:43.669
Well. that's what
she would have said.

80
00:04:43.717 --> 00:04:50.822
<i>♪ ♪</i>

81
00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:58.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

82
00:05:10.944 --> 00:05:15.146
<i>♪ ♪</i>

83
00:05:15.590 --> 00:05:19.016
soldier. move away
from the gold.

84
00:05:21.575 --> 00:05:23.566
What are you doing?

85
00:05:23.808 --> 00:05:25.711
The destruction is coming.

86
00:05:25.852 --> 00:05:28.118
Currency to protect my family.

87
00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:32.221
Yours too.

88
00:05:36.418 --> 00:05:38.770
Where's your Queen?

89
00:05:40.205 --> 00:05:47.311
<i>♪ ♪</i>

90
00:05:50.418 --> 00:05:53.939
Where is your Queen?

91
00:05:54.082 --> 00:05:57.789
<i>♪ ♪</i>

92
00:06:02.928 --> 00:06:10.034
<i>♪ ♪</i>

93
00:06:14.007 --> 00:06:21.078
<i>♪ ♪</i>

94
00:06:45.305 --> 00:06:52.410
<i>♪ ♪</i>

95
00:07:01.683 --> 00:07:03.321
If anyone comes...

96
00:07:13.511 --> 00:07:20.872
<i>♪ ♪</i>

97
00:07:37.122 --> 00:07:39.290
Lucas. not like this...

98
00:07:40.715 --> 00:07:42.237
Look at me!

99
00:07:42.418 --> 00:07:44.962
At least look at me!

100
00:07:59.457 --> 00:08:02.380
Now that I've got
all this witch stuff inside me.

101
00:08:02.382 --> 00:08:05.383
can't we just. you know.
fly to wherever?

102
00:08:05.385 --> 00:08:08.419
If we fly.
Glinda will find out about you.

103
00:08:08.421 --> 00:08:10.288
Then she'll want you
for her own.

104
00:08:10.290 --> 00:08:12.256
Why would she want me?

105
00:08:12.258 --> 00:08:15.426
You have the powers
of a cardinal witch.

106
00:08:15.428 --> 00:08:17.395
It's a force
to be reckoned with.

107
00:08:17.397 --> 00:08:19.263
I don't feel like it.

108
00:08:19.265 --> 00:08:21.966
I don't feel any magic.

109
00:08:27.439 --> 00:08:30.708
And what does that feel like?

110
00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:32.944
Like...

111
00:08:36.316 --> 00:08:37.965
Nothing.

112
00:08:38.160 --> 00:08:39.834
I died and came back to life.

113
00:08:39.882 --> 00:08:42.683
Surely I can cast
a stupid spell.

114
00:08:44.207 --> 00:08:47.558
You don't summon magic.

115
00:08:49.011 --> 00:08:50.590
It comes for you.

116
00:08:50.697 --> 00:08:53.230
How?

117
00:08:53.434 --> 00:08:55.467
Sit down.

118
00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:03.441
Close your eyes.

119
00:09:07.546 --> 00:09:10.982
Now tell me. what do you feel?

120
00:09:15.454 --> 00:09:17.488
Hatred.

121
00:09:17.490 --> 00:09:20.458
For the Wizard and the man
who killed my family.

122
00:09:20.460 --> 00:09:23.194
Absorb it.

123
00:09:23.196 --> 00:09:25.629
Take it with you.

124
00:09:25.631 --> 00:09:27.631
Then go deeper still.

125
00:09:29.736 --> 00:09:32.370
Something's happening.
I-i can't stop it.

126
00:09:32.372 --> 00:09:34.739
You're not supposed to.

127
00:09:37.744 --> 00:09:45.016
<i>♪ ♪</i>

128
00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:11.509
how did you do that?

129
00:10:11.511 --> 00:10:13.511
I didn't.

130
00:10:15.380 --> 00:10:17.548
This is what the magic found.

131
00:10:17.550 --> 00:10:19.550
This is me!

132
00:10:35.667 --> 00:10:37.401
Why?

133
00:10:39.704 --> 00:10:42.339
You should have never been.

134
00:10:42.341 --> 00:10:44.075
But I am.

135
00:10:44.077 --> 00:10:45.810
You should have never happened.

136
00:10:45.812 --> 00:10:51.082
I'd send you home if I could.
but it's not possible.

137
00:10:51.084 --> 00:10:54.318
Neither we were before we fell
into this world. but I did.

138
00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:56.554
And it's wrong.

139
00:10:56.556 --> 00:10:59.123
You being here...
you...

140
00:10:59.125 --> 00:11:02.526
you can't be part of me.

141
00:11:02.528 --> 00:11:04.428
You can't.

142
00:11:04.430 --> 00:11:06.597
Not anymore.

143
00:11:06.599 --> 00:11:08.666
So do it.

144
00:11:08.668 --> 00:11:10.634
Kill me.

145
00:11:10.636 --> 00:11:14.029
Do it.
Do it!

146
00:11:14.221 --> 00:11:16.088
Do it!

147
00:11:16.309 --> 00:11:19.877
<i>♪ ♪</i>

148
00:11:20.396 --> 00:11:22.646
you can't. can you?

149
00:11:29.354 --> 00:11:31.522
Close your eyes.

150
00:11:34.626 --> 00:11:37.528
Close your eyes.

151
00:11:39.292 --> 00:11:41.026
Ahh!

152
00:11:53.745 --> 00:12:00.818
<i>♪ ♪</i>

153
00:12:18.770 --> 00:12:22.406
Stop me!
Dorothy. please. stop me!

154
00:12:22.408 --> 00:12:25.442
Use the gauntlets. please!

155
00:12:25.444 --> 00:12:26.744
Stop me!

156
00:12:26.746 --> 00:12:28.212
I can't.

157
00:12:28.214 --> 00:12:29.813
I don't want you dead...

158
00:12:29.815 --> 00:12:31.749
I don't want you dead.

159
00:12:32.852 --> 00:12:35.686
Stop me. Dorothy!

160
00:12:35.688 --> 00:12:38.222
Stop me!

161
00:12:38.224 --> 00:12:42.593
<i>♪ ♪</i>

162
00:13:02.681 --> 00:13:04.815
No...

163
00:13:48.293 --> 00:13:50.294
You got your wish.

164
00:13:58.837 --> 00:14:01.438
I never happened to you.

165
00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:08.545
<i>♪ ♪</i>

166
00:14:25.031 --> 00:14:32.336
<i>♪ ♪</i>

167
00:14:34.873 --> 00:14:36.507
you have my gold.

168
00:14:36.509 --> 00:14:38.475
And your guns.

169
00:14:38.477 --> 00:14:40.511
Do you wonder
why you're still alive

170
00:14:40.513 --> 00:14:44.081
when these men in this room have
killed everyone else around you?

171
00:14:44.083 --> 00:14:46.083
If you kill me.

172
00:14:46.085 --> 00:14:48.352
my soldiers kill yours.

173
00:14:48.354 --> 00:14:50.621
You've lost your army
to fight Glinda.

174
00:14:50.623 --> 00:14:52.323
The end.

175
00:14:55.460 --> 00:14:57.494
I see you're very smart.

176
00:15:00.465 --> 00:15:07.104
<i>♪ ♪</i>

177
00:15:07.106 --> 00:15:09.540
you're a clever girl.

178
00:15:13.445 --> 00:15:15.012
Ahh!

179
00:15:19.085 --> 00:15:26.390
<i>♪ ♪</i>

180
00:15:29.494 --> 00:15:33.397
I know your father is
no longer around to teach you.

181
00:15:33.399 --> 00:15:38.502
So let me give you a lesson
in how to negotiate properly.

182
00:15:38.504 --> 00:15:41.739
You make yourself presentable
for your soldiers.

183
00:15:41.741 --> 00:15:45.008
And choose a new mask.

184
00:15:48.546 --> 00:15:50.547
It might be your last.

185
00:15:52.117 --> 00:15:54.051
Jane!

186
00:15:54.053 --> 00:15:56.520
Jane! Jane. you have to help!

187
00:15:56.522 --> 00:15:57.988
What happened?

188
00:15:57.990 --> 00:15:59.656
The Wizard and his men
have langwidere.

189
00:15:59.658 --> 00:16:01.158
The Wizard is here?

190
00:16:01.160 --> 00:16:02.659
If her soldiers don't
turn over the guns.

191
00:16:02.661 --> 00:16:04.161
he's going to execute her.

192
00:16:07.399 --> 00:16:08.699
What do we do?

193
00:16:10.702 --> 00:16:12.102
Jane!

194
00:16:23.515 --> 00:16:26.116
You hold the power
of my sacred sister.

195
00:16:26.118 --> 00:16:27.651
most merciful and stern.

196
00:16:27.653 --> 00:16:29.453
Try to be worthy.

197
00:16:29.455 --> 00:16:32.456
I've never felt better.

198
00:16:34.092 --> 00:16:35.759
I'm free.

199
00:16:35.761 --> 00:16:38.095
I'll split you in two
if you touch me with those.

200
00:16:38.097 --> 00:16:39.830
That's what we'll do
to the Wizard.

201
00:16:39.832 --> 00:16:42.032
Tear him in two.
Oh. grow up.

202
00:16:42.034 --> 00:16:44.435
Two witches aren't just going to
walk into emerald city

203
00:16:44.437 --> 00:16:46.103
and unseat the Wizard alone.

204
00:16:46.105 --> 00:16:48.739
Fine.
What else do we need?

205
00:16:48.741 --> 00:16:51.108
Supporters.

206
00:16:51.110 --> 00:16:53.710
Your father had many
and that's who we'll recruit.

207
00:16:53.712 --> 00:16:55.612
Then let's go.

208
00:16:58.149 --> 00:16:59.750
What?

209
00:16:59.752 --> 00:17:01.618
You can't go like that.

210
00:17:01.620 --> 00:17:03.754
Like what?

211
00:17:03.756 --> 00:17:06.123
A boy.

212
00:17:06.125 --> 00:17:08.826
Ozma was born a girl.

213
00:17:08.828 --> 00:17:11.495
But...

214
00:17:11.497 --> 00:17:15.466
This is what I've always been.

215
00:17:15.468 --> 00:17:17.468
This is who I really am.

216
00:17:17.470 --> 00:17:19.036
You were born a girl.

217
00:17:19.038 --> 00:17:21.171
And if you don't change yourself
back into one.

218
00:17:21.173 --> 00:17:22.639
no one will follow you.

219
00:17:22.641 --> 00:17:24.074
You will never have
your revenge.

220
00:17:24.076 --> 00:17:26.610
I finally have
what I care about most.

221
00:17:26.612 --> 00:17:28.846
Emerald city. the throne.
that's what you want.

222
00:17:28.848 --> 00:17:31.648
That's why I gave you
my sister's powers!

223
00:17:31.650 --> 00:17:33.617
Not for your own
petty indulgences.

224
00:17:33.619 --> 00:17:35.786
This isn't petty!
This is me!

225
00:17:35.788 --> 00:17:37.187
So your parents will
go unavenged

226
00:17:37.189 --> 00:17:38.789
just so you can take a piss
standing up?

227
00:17:38.791 --> 00:17:41.091
Don't!

228
00:17:41.093 --> 00:17:42.860
Don't.

229
00:17:45.663 --> 00:17:47.698
Don't do this to me.

230
00:17:47.700 --> 00:17:50.501
Don't make me choose.

231
00:17:54.906 --> 00:17:58.242
Do you have any idea

232
00:17:58.244 --> 00:18:01.078
what it was like for me

233
00:18:01.080 --> 00:18:04.214
to look in the mirror and see
a stranger staring back?

234
00:18:04.216 --> 00:18:08.852
To have someone else
all over me. infecting me?

235
00:18:08.854 --> 00:18:12.923
This... this...
this skin...

236
00:18:12.925 --> 00:18:17.528
it's the only thing
that was ever really mine.

237
00:18:18.930 --> 00:18:20.564
Tip.

238
00:18:20.566 --> 00:18:27.671
<i>♪ ♪</i>

239
00:18:42.855 --> 00:18:46.924
Yeah. I know. I'm trespass.
I remember.

240
00:18:48.793 --> 00:18:51.194
I don't want trouble
with any of you.

241
00:18:53.865 --> 00:18:55.332
I want ojo.

242
00:19:08.747 --> 00:19:11.582
Why did you take to a witch
who wanted to kill me?

243
00:19:11.584 --> 00:19:13.684
Because the one from the west
almost did.

244
00:19:13.686 --> 00:19:15.953
- You are revenge.
- Answer me.

245
00:19:15.955 --> 00:19:19.256
To free my wife
from the prison of the abject.

246
00:19:19.258 --> 00:19:20.657
And did she?

247
00:19:22.293 --> 00:19:24.194
Her words were false.

248
00:19:24.196 --> 00:19:26.964
I want nahara free too.

249
00:19:29.267 --> 00:19:31.268
And I have the power to do it.

250
00:19:32.370 --> 00:19:34.638
What do you want from her?

251
00:19:34.640 --> 00:19:36.640
The stone giants.

252
00:19:36.642 --> 00:19:38.375
The eternal warriors.

253
00:19:38.377 --> 00:19:41.345
To stop Glinda permanently.

254
00:19:41.347 --> 00:19:45.315
It took magic to raise them.
and the Wizard doesn't have any.

255
00:19:49.320 --> 00:19:52.789
But nahara does. doesn't she?

256
00:19:55.439 --> 00:19:58.174
I want her to raise
the giants again.

257
00:19:58.364 --> 00:20:00.364
For the Wizard?

258
00:20:01.366 --> 00:20:02.833
For me.

259
00:20:14.113 --> 00:20:21.218
<i>♪ ♪</i>

260
00:20:21.880 --> 00:20:23.013
we're done.

261
00:20:24.430 --> 00:20:25.697
Go your own way.

262
00:20:28.159 --> 00:20:30.293
Without you. there is no army.

263
00:20:30.295 --> 00:20:33.830
Without ozma. there is no oz.

264
00:20:35.867 --> 00:20:37.267
What does that mean?

265
00:20:37.269 --> 00:20:39.936
We'll try it your way.

266
00:20:39.938 --> 00:20:41.204
As a boy.

267
00:20:41.206 --> 00:20:43.040
Thank you.

268
00:20:47.011 --> 00:20:50.080
Thank you for understanding me.

269
00:20:50.082 --> 00:20:57.187
<i>♪ ♪</i>

270
00:21:02.061 --> 00:21:09.166
<i>♪ ♪</i>

271
00:21:13.838 --> 00:21:15.038
frank?

272
00:21:15.087 --> 00:21:16.386
Frank? Who's that?

273
00:21:18.976 --> 00:21:21.696
It's familiar.
But lost.

274
00:21:21.947 --> 00:21:25.882
So was everyone I cared about
when you damned me to live here.

275
00:21:28.953 --> 00:21:32.355
You were never kind to me. Jane.

276
00:21:33.823 --> 00:21:35.790
Do you remember?

277
00:21:37.161 --> 00:21:40.828
Despite how much
I tried to help you

278
00:21:40.933 --> 00:21:42.899
be who you were.

279
00:21:42.901 --> 00:21:44.255
It was your job to help me.

280
00:21:44.303 --> 00:21:47.304
Yet you didn't help me
when we found oz.

281
00:21:47.352 --> 00:21:49.039
When it was my time.

282
00:21:49.108 --> 00:21:51.262
You even discredited me.

283
00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:55.066
I'm the only one left
who knows you're a fraud.

284
00:21:55.493 --> 00:21:58.235
It must hurt

285
00:21:58.453 --> 00:22:00.350
to know that no one will listen.

286
00:22:02.186 --> 00:22:05.422
I know the only reason
you have kept me alive

287
00:22:05.424 --> 00:22:10.160
is because my work has value
to you.

288
00:22:10.162 --> 00:22:12.262
Tell me what you need.

289
00:22:12.264 --> 00:22:14.931
I-I'll make it for you now.

290
00:22:21.906 --> 00:22:24.941
You came here
to save langwidere.

291
00:22:24.943 --> 00:22:26.877
How very maternal of you.

292
00:22:26.879 --> 00:22:28.445
She is just a girl!

293
00:22:28.447 --> 00:22:30.947
She's standing
in the way of survival.

294
00:22:30.949 --> 00:22:32.983
Frank. you have taken
everything else from me.

295
00:22:32.985 --> 00:22:34.317
Not this too.
You can't!

296
00:22:34.319 --> 00:22:36.920
I am the Wizard of oz!

297
00:22:38.289 --> 00:22:43.326
If you call me any name
other than that again...

298
00:22:43.328 --> 00:22:47.164
Won't be her life
that you're begging for.

299
00:23:02.113 --> 00:23:04.414
He can't be stopped.

300
00:23:06.083 --> 00:23:08.485
He'll destroy everything
for those guns.

301
00:23:10.888 --> 00:23:13.356
Then make me the gun.

302
00:23:21.299 --> 00:23:23.867
Why did you lie to me?

303
00:23:23.869 --> 00:23:28.872
When we first met. you told me
the Wizard animated the giants.

304
00:23:28.874 --> 00:23:31.007
He would have burnt
the tribal freelands

305
00:23:31.009 --> 00:23:32.309
if I spoke truth.

306
00:23:32.311 --> 00:23:35.111
That's why he imprisoned nahara?

307
00:23:36.881 --> 00:23:38.315
To keep his secret.

308
00:23:38.317 --> 00:23:40.984
Yes.

309
00:23:40.986 --> 00:23:44.020
Nahara was sacrifice.

310
00:23:44.022 --> 00:23:46.990
So our people lived.

311
00:23:46.992 --> 00:23:49.359
Ojo. you deserve
to see her again.

312
00:23:49.361 --> 00:23:51.428
To have her home.

313
00:23:57.369 --> 00:24:00.474
Torrent downloaded from RARBG

314
00:24:12.016 --> 00:24:15.051
you'll bring nahara to me?

315
00:24:15.053 --> 00:24:16.953
Yes.

316
00:24:16.955 --> 00:24:19.322
but I'm not just gonna free
nahara.

317
00:24:19.324 --> 00:24:21.524
I'm gonna free all of them.

318
00:24:21.526 --> 00:24:28.999
<i>♪ ♪</i>

319
00:24:32.971 --> 00:24:40.076
<i>♪ ♪</i>

320
00:24:57.094 --> 00:25:04.200
<i>♪ ♪</i>

321
00:25:06.170 --> 00:25:07.570
what happened to the witches?

322
00:25:07.572 --> 00:25:10.106
Free me...

323
00:25:10.108 --> 00:25:12.475
And I'll tell you.

324
00:25:30.328 --> 00:25:33.396
Nahara... is... is she...

325
00:25:33.398 --> 00:25:36.166
Only the sick and dying remain.

326
00:25:36.168 --> 00:25:38.435
The rest of the prisoners.
where are they?

327
00:25:38.437 --> 00:25:40.603
Taken.

328
00:25:42.173 --> 00:25:44.441
Taken? Taken by who?

329
00:25:44.443 --> 00:25:47.577
Your army of witches.

330
00:25:47.579 --> 00:25:50.146
Your army of magic.

331
00:25:50.148 --> 00:25:52.415
Dressed and ready for war!

332
00:25:52.417 --> 00:25:59.522
<i>♪ ♪</i>

333
00:26:08.599 --> 00:26:11.067
I'm sorry. ojo.

334
00:26:13.604 --> 00:26:15.472
Nahara...

335
00:26:23.681 --> 00:26:26.616
West took everyone
but the dead and dying.

336
00:26:48.039 --> 00:26:50.774
I'm Dorothy Gale.
I ripped the sky.

337
00:26:54.812 --> 00:26:58.181
Nahara...

338
00:26:58.183 --> 00:27:01.251
I need you to raise
the eternal warriors for me.

339
00:27:15.599 --> 00:27:17.801
It will not be done.

340
00:27:20.071 --> 00:27:21.671
It's the only way
to stop the war

341
00:27:21.673 --> 00:27:23.273
between Glinda and the Wizard.

342
00:27:36.687 --> 00:27:38.688
War is good.

343
00:27:38.690 --> 00:27:39.756
No. No.

344
00:27:39.758 --> 00:27:42.158
People will be killed. nahara.

345
00:27:42.160 --> 00:27:44.761
Children will be killed.

346
00:28:00.144 --> 00:28:02.245
Oz is magic.

347
00:28:02.247 --> 00:28:04.881
The Wizard is death.
Yes.

348
00:28:04.883 --> 00:28:06.649
But if I help the Wizard.

349
00:28:06.651 --> 00:28:08.551
he's gonna take me
back to where I belong.

350
00:28:08.553 --> 00:28:12.155
And if you help me.
I'll take the Wizard with me.

351
00:28:14.258 --> 00:28:16.226
Free magic?

352
00:28:16.228 --> 00:28:18.628
Yes.

353
00:28:18.630 --> 00:28:20.663
Free magic.

354
00:28:28.572 --> 00:28:31.141
This is why you had me drink
east's spells.

355
00:28:31.143 --> 00:28:32.909
Not for me.

356
00:28:32.911 --> 00:28:35.278
You just wanted her magic
so you could free your sisters.

357
00:28:35.280 --> 00:28:37.680
I wanted you to have power.

358
00:28:37.682 --> 00:28:41.651
Be it magic. riches. or an army.
it makes no different.

359
00:28:41.653 --> 00:28:44.187
You take power
where you can find it.

360
00:28:45.823 --> 00:28:49.225
Their magic will unite with ours
to end the Wizard for good.

361
00:28:51.228 --> 00:28:53.763
How do you know
they'll follow me?

362
00:28:53.765 --> 00:28:56.266
I'll make them.

363
00:28:56.268 --> 00:29:01.171
In certain circles. I was known
as the wicked witch of the west.

364
00:29:01.173 --> 00:29:04.674
Yeah. I heard that.

365
00:29:15.719 --> 00:29:19.722
As you once stood united
with king pastoria.

366
00:29:19.724 --> 00:29:22.325
you now stand with his child.

367
00:29:22.327 --> 00:29:25.862
the one true heir
to the throne. ozma.

368
00:29:25.864 --> 00:29:27.931
Follow us to emerald city

369
00:29:27.933 --> 00:29:30.333
to end the one
who imprisoned you:

370
00:29:30.335 --> 00:29:32.835
The horrible Wizard of oz!

371
00:29:32.837 --> 00:29:34.737
Ozma is dead.

372
00:29:34.739 --> 00:29:36.706
It's a boy in a dress!

373
00:29:36.708 --> 00:29:39.409
What imposter
do you bring before us?

374
00:29:39.411 --> 00:29:42.879
He possesses the the emerald
dagger given by his father.

375
00:29:42.881 --> 00:29:46.249
None can question
its authenticity.

376
00:29:49.254 --> 00:29:50.987
It proves nothing.

377
00:29:50.989 --> 00:29:52.956
Possessions can be lost.

378
00:29:52.958 --> 00:29:54.824
And found.

379
00:29:54.826 --> 00:29:57.293
This boy is no ozma.

380
00:29:57.295 --> 00:30:00.430
I am a cardinal witch
and you will hear my truth

381
00:30:00.432 --> 00:30:02.232
or I'll gladly throw you
back in prison

382
00:30:02.234 --> 00:30:03.933
if you find it more agreeable.

383
00:30:03.935 --> 00:30:06.636
None here will be intimidated
by the Wizard's whore.

384
00:30:06.638 --> 00:30:08.771
- I'm nobody's whore.
- You're worse.

385
00:30:08.773 --> 00:30:12.976
You're a traitor.
and you will speak no more.

386
00:30:12.978 --> 00:30:15.712
Mistress!

387
00:30:30.794 --> 00:30:33.363
Are you ready. little Queen?

388
00:30:35.266 --> 00:30:37.500
I hope you've chosen wisely.

389
00:30:40.738 --> 00:30:42.405
I have.

390
00:30:46.944 --> 00:30:48.478
The Queen!

391
00:30:48.480 --> 00:30:50.446
Ready your weapons!

392
00:30:50.448 --> 00:30:53.316
Be calm!
I am sound.

393
00:30:56.787 --> 00:31:00.323
And though exposed.
it is of my own choosing.

394
00:31:00.325 --> 00:31:03.393
Tell them to put down
their guns and join us.

395
00:31:04.328 --> 00:31:05.795
Tell them

396
00:31:05.797 --> 00:31:07.463
or you die.

397
00:31:07.465 --> 00:31:10.366
Then you get nothing.

398
00:31:11.435 --> 00:31:13.836
Why don't you try
and convince them?

399
00:31:16.907 --> 00:31:18.875
Soldiers of ev.

400
00:31:18.877 --> 00:31:22.312
we can fight together

401
00:31:22.314 --> 00:31:24.514
or we can die apart.

402
00:31:24.516 --> 00:31:28.051
And the first death

403
00:31:28.053 --> 00:31:31.988
will be the most tragic
and unnecessary death

404
00:31:31.990 --> 00:31:33.823
of your Queen

405
00:31:33.825 --> 00:31:36.559
if you don't put down
your weapons.

406
00:31:38.762 --> 00:31:40.029
Madame Queen?

407
00:31:40.031 --> 00:31:42.365
What is your wish?

408
00:31:42.367 --> 00:31:45.034
Last chance to save your life.

409
00:31:50.474 --> 00:31:53.343
Let us be...

410
00:31:53.345 --> 00:31:55.812
An example.

411
00:31:55.814 --> 00:31:58.381
My life is worth nothing

412
00:31:58.383 --> 00:32:01.818
unless you stand with me
against this man.

413
00:32:01.820 --> 00:32:03.753
Never surrender your weapons!

414
00:32:03.755 --> 00:32:05.388
Oh. you put them down!

415
00:32:05.390 --> 00:32:09.025
You put your guns down
or your Queen is lost!

416
00:32:09.027 --> 00:32:10.093
Do you understand?

417
00:32:10.095 --> 00:32:12.028
If you make me kill her.

418
00:32:12.030 --> 00:32:14.430
you all die.

419
00:32:16.433 --> 00:32:18.134
It's okay.

420
00:32:20.504 --> 00:32:22.572
Let me go.

421
00:32:29.381 --> 00:32:32.815
<i>♪ ♪</i>

422
00:32:32.817 --> 00:32:33.816
no.

423
00:32:33.818 --> 00:32:37.053
<i>♪ ♪</i>

424
00:32:40.158 --> 00:32:41.557
Stop him!

425
00:32:41.559 --> 00:32:48.664
<i>♪ ♪</i>

426
00:33:00.944 --> 00:33:03.446
I'm here.
I'm here.

427
00:34:14.585 --> 00:34:15.952
Ojo!

428
00:34:22.192 --> 00:34:23.893
Jane!

429
00:34:23.895 --> 00:34:26.662
Jane. she's been shot.
You have to do something.

430
00:34:26.664 --> 00:34:28.564
You have to help her!

431
00:34:29.633 --> 00:34:30.967
Fix her!

432
00:34:30.969 --> 00:34:32.802
You have to do something!
Please. fix her!

433
00:34:32.804 --> 00:34:36.005
Fix her like you fixed me.

434
00:34:36.007 --> 00:34:38.174
Please!

435
00:34:38.176 --> 00:34:41.644
<i>♪ ♪</i>

436
00:34:41.646 --> 00:34:42.778
she can't die!

437
00:34:42.780 --> 00:34:45.515
Do for her what you did for me.

438
00:34:45.517 --> 00:34:47.717
You were alive
when we found you.

439
00:34:47.719 --> 00:34:49.519
So is she!

440
00:34:50.787 --> 00:34:52.188
So is she!

441
00:34:52.190 --> 00:34:54.023
No. Jack...

442
00:34:54.025 --> 00:34:56.792
no!
So is she!

443
00:34:56.794 --> 00:34:58.828
Jack!

444
00:35:04.935 --> 00:35:06.569
Because we are fair.

445
00:35:06.571 --> 00:35:08.604
you will hear
the charges against you

446
00:35:08.606 --> 00:35:09.972
before you are sentenced.

447
00:35:09.974 --> 00:35:13.609
More than your apostate
of a sister did for us.

448
00:35:13.611 --> 00:35:15.978
You and your cardinal sisters

449
00:35:15.980 --> 00:35:19.015
are to blame for the end
of our kind.

450
00:35:19.017 --> 00:35:21.617
She stands against her sisters.

451
00:35:21.619 --> 00:35:25.021
It was mistress east
who locked you in the prison.

452
00:35:25.023 --> 00:35:28.724
But mistress west
sold the soul of our world

453
00:35:28.726 --> 00:35:30.593
for her own escape.

454
00:35:30.595 --> 00:35:32.728
to forget her pain.

455
00:35:32.730 --> 00:35:35.831
She was weak. as we all are.

456
00:35:35.833 --> 00:35:39.035
She set herself apart from us.
denied us our place.

457
00:35:39.037 --> 00:35:42.638
Now she will pay
for the sins of her sisters.

458
00:35:42.640 --> 00:35:45.274
those here and gone.

459
00:36:05.629 --> 00:36:08.598
Help your sister to her feet.

460
00:36:08.600 --> 00:36:12.301
Shapeshifting and sound waves.

461
00:36:12.303 --> 00:36:14.737
Both base magics.

462
00:36:31.321 --> 00:36:32.922
It's going to be okay.

463
00:36:32.924 --> 00:36:34.624
Everything's going to be okay.

464
00:36:39.763 --> 00:36:41.731
Wait. wait. wait. wait!

465
00:36:55.345 --> 00:36:58.014
<i>♪ ♪</i>

466
00:37:01.019 --> 00:37:03.386
<i>♪ ♪</i>

467
00:37:08.959 --> 00:37:11.927
this magic can't be tricked.

468
00:37:11.929 --> 00:37:13.863
You are true.

469
00:37:14.931 --> 00:37:18.067
We honor king pastoria

470
00:37:18.069 --> 00:37:20.169
and his daughter.

471
00:37:21.371 --> 00:37:24.840
Mistress west freed your hides.

472
00:37:24.842 --> 00:37:29.679
She stands against those who
truly act again the sisterhood.

473
00:37:29.681 --> 00:37:33.683
So help her to her feet.

474
00:37:33.685 --> 00:37:36.852
The Wizard has oppressed the
magic that is your birthright...

475
00:37:36.854 --> 00:37:39.955
its seeds sown into
the fabric of this land.

476
00:37:39.957 --> 00:37:42.958
No one can take that away
from you.

477
00:37:42.960 --> 00:37:45.761
Fight with me to rise again.

478
00:37:45.763 --> 00:37:49.098
To emerald city.

479
00:37:54.838 --> 00:37:57.807
How many masks did you make her?

480
00:37:57.809 --> 00:37:59.442
- Jack...
- how many?

481
00:37:59.444 --> 00:38:01.243
Hundreds.

482
00:38:02.179 --> 00:38:05.848
One for sadness.

483
00:38:05.850 --> 00:38:07.917
For joy.

484
00:38:07.919 --> 00:38:10.052
One for rage.

485
00:38:11.054 --> 00:38:12.922
For longing.

486
00:38:14.191 --> 00:38:16.158
One for love.

487
00:38:19.096 --> 00:38:22.798
She tried to love you. Jack.
as best she could.

488
00:38:23.767 --> 00:38:25.134
Did you make one for this?

489
00:38:25.136 --> 00:38:28.070
For death?

490
00:38:28.072 --> 00:38:29.739
No.

491
00:38:30.774 --> 00:38:33.175
- I killed her. Jane.
- No.

492
00:38:33.177 --> 00:38:36.045
- This is all my fault.
- You didn't kill her.

493
00:38:36.047 --> 00:38:37.913
I shot her!

494
00:38:37.915 --> 00:38:39.782
I killed her!

495
00:38:46.423 --> 00:38:48.023
Many years ago.

496
00:38:48.025 --> 00:38:51.260
the beast forever
destroyed this kingdom.

497
00:38:51.262 --> 00:38:52.795
Jane.

498
00:38:54.030 --> 00:38:56.499
Slaughtered the royal family.

499
00:38:56.501 --> 00:39:00.069
What are you doing?

500
00:39:00.071 --> 00:39:03.873
The Queen...

501
00:39:03.875 --> 00:39:05.941
Her sons...

502
00:39:08.278 --> 00:39:10.846
Her daughter.

503
00:39:10.848 --> 00:39:12.248
And what of him?

504
00:39:12.250 --> 00:39:15.251
Only the king survived.

505
00:39:17.788 --> 00:39:19.121
I don't understand.

506
00:39:19.123 --> 00:39:22.191
You didn't kill her. Jack.

507
00:39:22.193 --> 00:39:26.028
Because she was already dead.

508
00:39:32.936 --> 00:39:35.871
I salvaged what remained.

509
00:39:35.873 --> 00:39:38.808
The rest. I rebuilt.

510
00:39:38.810 --> 00:39:42.278
I made her masks to hide a face
that never aged.

511
00:39:42.280 --> 00:39:45.214
It was a secret
the king swore me to keep.

512
00:39:45.216 --> 00:39:49.118
He couldn't lose her.
and you don't have to either.

513
00:39:49.120 --> 00:39:50.820
I can repair her.

514
00:39:50.822 --> 00:39:54.056
You let me believe she was real!

515
00:39:54.058 --> 00:39:55.825
That I was real!

516
00:39:55.827 --> 00:39:58.928
- You are.
- No. I'm not!

517
00:39:58.930 --> 00:40:01.096
I'm nothing but tin. like her.

518
00:40:01.098 --> 00:40:04.133
- No!
- This body. these parts...

519
00:40:04.135 --> 00:40:05.234
No.

520
00:40:06.570 --> 00:40:10.039
I might as well
put them to good use.

521
00:40:10.041 --> 00:40:12.141
Where are you going?

522
00:40:13.977 --> 00:40:15.511
To cut down the Wizard.

523
00:40:15.513 --> 00:40:16.979
His soldiers will kill you.

524
00:40:16.981 --> 00:40:18.514
They can't!

525
00:40:18.516 --> 00:40:21.517
I'm already dead.

526
00:40:21.519 --> 00:40:23.853
Jack! Wait!

527
00:40:51.214 --> 00:40:53.082
Positions!

528
00:40:54.117 --> 00:40:56.051
Aim.
No!

529
00:40:57.087 --> 00:40:59.588
Please.

530
00:41:05.596 --> 00:41:08.597
<i>♪ ♪</i>

531
00:41:16.140 --> 00:41:23.245
<i>♪ ♪</i>

532
00:41:33.590 --> 00:41:40.696
<i>♪ ♪</i>

532
